name: Puking Nostalgia
description:
A polar bear father, Rufus, has had enough of his friends' behavior. They laughed at him, sillied him, and then told him that his offspring wouldn't survive next decade. Although half joke, Rufus took it rather seriously then went to solitude.
Feeling mad and sad, Rufus pukes. He decides to return all things humans gave him, humans think as fun and nostalgia.
Their relationship will never be the same again.

JPEG, 2400 x 2400 px.
